<subSubSection pageId="3" pageNumber="598" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="3.[167,1374,2975,3481]" pageId="3" pageNumber="598">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[169,521,3369,3402]" pageId="3" pageNumber="598">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Not assessed on The IUCN Red List, whereit is considered a synonym of 
<taxonomicName box="[343,470,3408,3441]" class="Mammalia" family="Talpidae" genus="Uropsilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Soricomorpha" pageId="3" pageNumber="598" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="gracilis">U. gracilis</taxonomicName>
, which is classified as Least Concern.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
